data.text: Auburn Hills is a family-friendly community that is both quiet and spacious. There is an on-site basketball court, and playground with multiple grassy areas to hang out in the summer! A beautiful creek runs right along the southern side of the community. Downtown Auburn is located only 2.5 miles away. Contact the on-site manager today!
